<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>AI at Work — Case Studies</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #F9F6F0;
    --ink: #1A1814;
    --ink-muted: #6B6760;
    --ink-faint: #B0ADA8;
    --accent: #D4522A;
    --accent-light: #FAE8E1;
    --green: #2A6B4A;
    --green-light: #E4F0EB;
    --amber: #B87514;
    --amber-light: #FBF0DA;
    --blue: #2055A4;
    --blue-light: #E4ECFA;
    --border: rgba(26,24,20,0.1);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(249,246,240,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    height: 56px;
  }
  .nav-brand { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-brand span { color: var(--accent); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .nav-link {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px; color: var(--ink-muted);
    cursor: pointer; border: none; background: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-link:hover { background: rgba(26,24,20,0.06); color: var(--ink); }
  .nav-link.active { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 2rem 3.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-light);
    padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink-muted);
    max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-rule {
    width: 48px; height: 2px;
    background: var(--accent); margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* TABS */
  .tabs-wrap {
    max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem 1rem;
    display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .tab-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: white; cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-muted);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .tab-btn:hover { border-color: rgba(26,24,20,0.25); color: var(--ink); }
  .tab-btn.active { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); border-color: var(--ink); }
  .tab-btn .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }

  /* CASE PANELS */
  .cases-wrap { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 6rem; }
  .case-panel { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }
  .case-panel.visible { display: block; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: none; } }

  /* BIZ HEADER */
  .biz-header {
    background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    gap: 1.5rem; align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .biz-emoji {
    width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 14px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 28px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .biz-meta h2 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .biz-meta p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-muted); line-height: 1.55; }
  .biz-tag {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px; white-space: nowrap;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  /* CORE VS NOT */
  .focus-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .focus-box {
    background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .focus-box-label {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .focus-box-label.green { color: var(--green); }
  .focus-box-label.red { color: var(--accent); }
  .pill-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .pill {
    font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px; border: 1px solid;
  }
  .pill.green { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); border-color: #b2d4c3; }
  .pill.red { background: var(--accent-light); color: var(--accent); border-color: #f0bfaf; }

  /* SECTION LABEL */
  .sec-label {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .sec-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

  /* PAIN CARDS */
  .pain-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pain-card {
    background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
    gap: 1rem; align-items: start;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .pain-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,24,20,0.07); }
  .pain-num {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .pain-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .pain-detail { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pain-quote {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-faint);
    padding-left: 12px; border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* OPPORTUNITY BOX */
  .opp-box {
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid;
  }
  .opp-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .opp-icon { font-size: 20px; }
  .opp-headline { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; }
  .opp-body { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .opp-services { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .opp-service {
    font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px; border: 1px solid;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .opp-pricing {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .opp-pricing strong { font-size: 17px; }

  /* PROMPT BOX */
  .prompt-box {
    background: var(--ink); border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 1rem; align-items: start;
  }
  .prompt-icon { font-size: 18px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .prompt-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.07em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8A9A7E; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .prompt-text { font-size: 14px; color: #E8E4DC; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center; padding: 2rem;
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  footer strong { color: var(--ink-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .biz-header { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; }
    .biz-tag { display: none; }
    .focus-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { padding: 0 1rem; }
    .hero { padding: 3rem 1.5rem 2.5rem; }
    .tabs-wrap, .cases-wrap { padding-left: 1.25rem; padding-right: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a class="nav-brand" href="#"><span>AI</span> at Work</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <button class="nav-link active" onclick="show(0,this)">Coaching</button>
    <button class="nav-link" onclick="show(1,this)">Preschool</button>
    <button class="nav-link" onclick="show(2,this)">Bakery</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Week 3 · Case Studies</div>
  <h1>Real businesses.<br /><em>Real problems.</em><br />Your opportunity.</h1>
  <p>These owners are excellent at what they do. But there's work they still have to do — that has nothing to do with their skill. That's where you come in.</p>
  <div class="hero-rule"></div>
</section>

<div class="tabs-wrap">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="show(0,this)">
    <div class="dot" style="background:#2055A4"></div> Sharma Classes
  </button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show(1,this)">
    <div class="dot" style="background:#2A6B4A"></div> Little Blooms Preschool
  </button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show(2,this)">
    <div class="dot" style="background:#D4522A"></div> Priya's Home Bakery
  </button>
</div>

<div class="cases-wrap">

  <!-- CASE 1: COACHING -->
  <div class="case-panel visible" id="panel-0">
    <div class="biz-header">
      <div class="biz-emoji" style="background:#E4ECFA;">📚</div>
      <div class="biz-meta">
        <h2>Sharma Classes</h2>
        <p>Coaching center for Class 8–12 students. Run by one teacher with two part-time tutors. 60 students enrolled. Exam prep focused. No admin support.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="biz-tag" style="background:#E4ECFA; color:#2055A4;">Nagpur</div>
    </div>

    <div class="focus-row">
      <div class="focus-box">
        <div class="focus-box-label green">What he's paid to do</div>
        <div class="pill-list">
          <div class="pill green">Teach concepts</div>
          <div class="pill green">Clear student doubts</div>
          <div class="pill green">Guide exam strategy</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-box">
        <div class="focus-box-label red">What eats his evenings</div>
        <div class="pill-list">
          <div class="pill red">Writing test papers</div>
          <div class="pill red">Parent messages</div>
          <div class="pill red">Admission posts</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label">3 pain points</div>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#E4ECFA; color:#2055A4;">1</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Writing test papers every week</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">Every Sunday he creates a fresh question paper from scratch — pulling questions from memory and old textbooks. It takes 2–3 hours with no system and no templates. By Monday he's already exhausted.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"I spend more time making the test than reviewing the results."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#E4ECFA; color:#2055A4;">2</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Parent communication</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">Progress updates, fee reminders, batch change notices, exam schedules — all typed manually on WhatsApp. Repetitive and often delayed because it feels like extra work on top of teaching.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"Parents complain they don't hear from me. But when do I have time to write?"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#E4ECFA; color:#2055A4;">3</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Admission season content</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">New batch starting? He needs social media posts, a WhatsApp broadcast, a notice board poster. He either skips it or posts something plain that gets no response — and loses students to centers with better-looking content.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"I know I should promote more. I just don't know how to write these things."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="opp-box" style="background:#E4ECFA; border-color:#b2c8ee;">
      <div class="opp-header">
        <div class="opp-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="opp-headline" style="color:#2055A4;">Your opportunity as a student</div>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-body" style="color:#1a3870;">Sharma sir is brilliant at teaching. He just needs someone to handle everything that happens around the classroom. You can offer a monthly package that covers all three pain points — he approves, you produce.</div>
      <div class="opp-services">
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#2055A4; border-color:#b2c8ee;">Question paper templates per subject</div>
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#2055A4; border-color:#b2c8ee;">Parent message library (WhatsApp)</div>
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#2055A4; border-color:#b2c8ee;">4 admission posts per batch launch</div>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-pricing" style="background:white; color:#2055A4;">
        <span>Monthly fee:</span><strong>₹5,000 – ₹8,000</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prompt-box">
      <div class="prompt-icon">⚡</div>
      <div>
        <div class="prompt-label">Try this prompt live</div>
        <div class="prompt-text">"Create 8 MCQ questions on the Water Cycle for Class 7 Science. Four options each. Mark the correct answer. CBSE difficulty level."</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CASE 2: PRESCHOOL -->
  <div class="case-panel" id="panel-1">
    <div class="biz-header">
      <div class="biz-emoji" style="background:#E4F0EB;">🏫</div>
      <div class="biz-meta">
        <h2>Little Blooms Preschool</h2>
        <p>A new preschool started by a first-time owner. Catering to 2–5 year olds. Trying to fill 30 seats before opening day. No marketing background, no admin support.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="biz-tag" style="background:#E4F0EB; color:#2A6B4A;">Pune</div>
    </div>

    <div class="focus-row">
      <div class="focus-box">
        <div class="focus-box-label green">What she's paid to do</div>
        <div class="pill-list">
          <div class="pill green">Care for young children</div>
          <div class="pill green">Build a safe space</div>
          <div class="pill green">Earn parent trust</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-box">
        <div class="focus-box-label red">What overwhelms her mornings</div>
        <div class="pill-list">
          <div class="pill red">Promoting admissions</div>
          <div class="pill red">Answering same questions</div>
          <div class="pill red">Parent newsletters</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label">3 pain points</div>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#E4F0EB; color:#2A6B4A;">1</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Promoting admissions</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">She needs parents in her neighborhood to know the school exists. But writing Facebook posts and WhatsApp forwards feels hard — she doesn't know what to say or how to sound trustworthy. Her posts get no response.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"I know my school is good. I just can't explain it in words that make people call me."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#E4F0EB; color:#2A6B4A;">2</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Answering the same parent questions</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">Every inquiry call covers the same ground — timings, fees, what children learn, is food provided, teacher-child ratio. She's answering this 10 times a day with no FAQ document and no saved message to share.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"I repeat myself on every call. By the 8th parent I'm exhausted before the day starts."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#E4F0EB; color:#2A6B4A;">3</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Monthly parent newsletters</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">Enrolled parents want to feel connected — what did kids learn this week, what's coming next month, any events. She knows this builds loyalty and reduces dropouts. But writing it consistently never happens.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"I take photos all day. But turning them into something to send parents — I never get around to it."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="opp-box" style="background:#E4F0EB; border-color:#b2d4c3;">
      <div class="opp-header">
        <div class="opp-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="opp-headline" style="color:#2A6B4A;">Your opportunity as a student</div>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-body" style="color:#1a4a31;">She's brilliant with children. The communication around the school is what's slipping. You can build her a simple content system she just maintains — while you produce all the first drafts.</div>
      <div class="opp-services">
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#2A6B4A; border-color:#b2d4c3;">5 admission posts per new batch</div>
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#2A6B4A; border-color:#b2d4c3;">Parent FAQ formatted for WhatsApp</div>
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#2A6B4A; border-color:#b2d4c3;">Monthly update template</div>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-pricing" style="background:white; color:#2A6B4A;">
        <span>Monthly fee:</span><strong>₹6,000 – ₹10,000</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prompt-box">
      <div class="prompt-icon">⚡</div>
      <div>
        <div class="prompt-label">Try this prompt live</div>
        <div class="prompt-text">"Write a warm WhatsApp message a preschool owner can send to parents who enquired about admissions. School name is Little Blooms, Pune. Keep it under 80 words. Friendly, not salesy."</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CASE 3: BAKERY -->
  <div class="case-panel" id="panel-2">
    <div class="biz-header">
      <div class="biz-emoji" style="background:#FAE8E1;">🎂</div>
      <div class="biz-meta">
        <h2>Priya's Home Bakery</h2>
        <p>A home baker selling custom cakes via Instagram and WhatsApp. Solo operation. Orders taken manually. Growing faster than she can manage alone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="biz-tag" style="background:#FAE8E1; color:#D4522A;">Mumbai</div>
    </div>

    <div class="focus-row">
      <div class="focus-box">
        <div class="focus-box-label green">What she's paid to do</div>
        <div class="pill-list">
          <div class="pill green">Bake and decorate</div>
          <div class="pill green">Deliver on time</div>
          <div class="pill green">Create custom designs</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-box">
        <div class="focus-box-label red">What pulls her from the kitchen</div>
        <div class="pill-list">
          <div class="pill red">Instagram every day</div>
          <div class="pill red">WhatsApp back-and-forth</div>
          <div class="pill red">Missing seasonal sales</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label">3 pain points</div>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#FAE8E1; color:#D4522A;">1</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Instagram content every day</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">She bakes beautiful things but posting them with the right caption, hashtags, and timing takes time she doesn't have. She either posts late, posts plainly, or skips days — which hurts her reach and order flow.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"I spend an hour baking something and five minutes posting it badly."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#FAE8E1; color:#D4522A;">2</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">WhatsApp order enquiries</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">Every order is a long back-and-forth — flavor, size, date, budget. She's typing the same questions to every customer. No standard order form, no saved replies. Conversations get lost. Orders get confused.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"I got two orders mixed up last month. The customers were upset. I was mortified."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-num" style="background:#FAE8E1; color:#D4522A;">3</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pain-title">Missing seasonal sales windows</div>
          <div class="pain-detail">Diwali boxes, Valentine's hampers, Christmas cakes — her biggest revenue moments. But planning the offers, writing the posts, creating the menu all happens last minute. She misses the window every time.</div>
          <div class="pain-quote">"By the time I post my Diwali offer, everyone has already ordered from someone else."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="opp-box" style="background:#FAE8E1; border-color:#f0bfaf;">
      <div class="opp-header">
        <div class="opp-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="opp-headline" style="color:#D4522A;">Your opportunity as a student</div>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-body" style="color:#7a2a12;">Priya's product sells itself — her cakes are beautiful. What she's missing is a content system and a sales rhythm. You can build both. And because your work directly connects to her sales, she'll feel the value immediately.</div>
      <div class="opp-services">
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#D4522A; border-color:#f0bfaf;">12 ready-to-post captions/month</div>
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#D4522A; border-color:#f0bfaf;">Standard WhatsApp order form</div>
        <div class="opp-service" style="background:white; color:#D4522A; border-color:#f0bfaf;">Seasonal campaign copy × 4/year</div>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-pricing" style="background:white; color:#D4522A;">
        <span>Monthly fee:</span><strong>₹5,000 – ₹8,000</strong>
      </div>
